{% comment %}
  Testimonials Section - Groovy World Homepage
  Shows customer reviews and testimonials
{% endcomment %}

<div class="testimonials-section" style="background: rgb(var(--color-background)); padding: 80px 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
    
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
      <h2 style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #333; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
        What Parents Say
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin: 0; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        Real stories from parents who have seen amazing improvements in their children's writing skills.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;">
      
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div style="background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background: #ff6b35; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 15px;">
            S
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">
              Sarah M.
            </h4>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
              <span style="color: #ffd700; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-right: 5px;">★★★★★</span>
              <span style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;">5.0</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">
          "My daughter was struggling with handwriting until we found Groovy Books. The fun exercises and colorful illustrations made learning enjoyable. Her handwriting has improved dramatically!"
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div style="background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background: #ff6b35; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 15px;">
            M
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">
              Michael R.
            </h4>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
              <span style="color: #ffd700; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-right: 5px;">★★★★★</span>
              <span style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;">5.0</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">
          "As a teacher, I've seen many handwriting programs, but Groovy Books is by far the most effective. The step-by-step approach and engaging content keep students motivated."
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div style="background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background: #ff6b35; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 15px;">
            L
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">
              Lisa K.
            </h4>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
              <span style="color: #ffd700; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-right: 5px;">★★★★★</span>
              <span style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;">5.0</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">
          "The progress tracking tools are amazing! I can see exactly how my son is improving. The books are well-structured and the quality is outstanding. Highly recommend!"
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Overall Rating -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 60px; padding: 40px; background: white; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
      <h3 style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin: 0 0 15px 0;">
        Trusted by Thousands of Parents
      </h3>
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <span style="color: #ffd700; font-size: 2rem; margin-right: 10px;">★★★★★</span>
        <span style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333;">4.9/5</span>
      </div>
      <p style="font-family: 'Preahvihear', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin: 0;">
        Based on 2,847 customer reviews
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

